  "description": "Sine strand spread thin across Poly8 voices through a trefoil knot. Very low braid depth — the web barely forms. Both LFOs at slow rates sculpt the open air around each note. High reverb mix dissolves the strand into pure atmosphere. This is ORBWEAVE as sky — topology dissolved into cloud.",
